{"tid":2421030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"啊波叔咁做唔怕比人央照肺？","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T08:52:39.000Z","uid":89227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd151d7e68309b6f566217839ea50bfa7bdfd09","tid":2421030,"uid":89227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中信證券統計，香港歷來股票印花稅調整後，港股多數下跌。其中，在1998年4月調整稅率後4個月，<span class=\"red\"><strong>恒指大跌44%</strong></span>；2000年4月調整稅率後2個月，恒指跌20%；恒指僅在2001年9月調整後4個月升30%。 實際買貴幾多？ 以一手100股、現價682元的騰訊 （00700）為例，在現時0.1%的稅率之下，買賣雙方均須付62.8元。但加稅後，雙方要付88.66元，印花稅大增。 中泰國際表示，現有的交易成本大約是0.25%+0.1077%=0.3577%，印花稅上調30%後，將令總交易成本上升至0.3877%，增加約8%。<br />\n<br />\n星期一（22號）先上左一隻匯添富中證滬港深500ETF<br />\n<br />\n跟踪的中證滬港深500指數更是融合了滬，港，深三市優質上市公司，可以更好地反映了中國經濟轉型發展的新方向 。<br />\n<br />\n據中證指數有限公司數據顯示，截至1月29日，該指數中<span class=\"red\"><strong>港股權重佔比為43.1％</strong></span>，A股重佔比為56.9％。 下，合併&ldquo;中概股&rdquo;不斷回歸，港股未來或會有突破的上升空間，港股重較高的滬港深500指數表現未來可期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dfscdn.dfcfw.com/download/D24670924854219996252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdfscdn.dfcfw.com%2Fdownload%2FD24670924854219996252.jpg&h=dbd4200c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dfscdn.dfcfw.com/download/D25273938235826153233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdfscdn.dfcfw.com%2Fdownload%2FD25273938235826153233.jpg&h=2b060883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n汁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/247317/?utm_campaign=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F247317%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dcopy&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d33c4f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/247317/?utm_campaign=copy</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.eastmoney.com/a/202102221815263944.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.eastmoney.com%2Fa%2F202102221815263944.html&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=efffda86\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.eastmoney.com/a/202102221815263944.html</a>"},{"pid":"9898a51ddab9169925525c5b0c2120eaf353493e","tid":2421030,"uid":30274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"緊係支共up左頭先會做啦<br />\n做之前緊係匯報晒, 讓領導先走<br />\n遲D跌完, 領導又入市架啦"},{"pid":"9717ff973e3371fece4852c6f9b10c9a9029f85d","tid":2421030,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:48:43.000Z","msg":"北水一早走左]"},{"pid":"e9f71f1139d6132906d64b64407ea7823d6a12cb","tid":2421030,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"搞到個巿閪冧俾位北水全面接管<br />\n順便幫中央懲治一下之前走資落嚟班走資派"},{"pid":"40265f7fa1bf8df467e88ab2894b7bb47dbe48ac","tid":2421030,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"即係一個股票  一定要賺超過0.8% 先開始盈利？"}]}